      The 'fileCreate' via POST (multipart form) implementation expects: the request suffix with the path of the files parent the 'file' part (form element / parameter) with the binary content an optional 'name' part (form element / parameter) name of the new resource The 'mix:versionable' type is set if not present and the 'jcr:lastModified' and 'jcr:mimeType' are adjusted.
